text: Jeffrey Wayne Fatt AM (born July 21, 1953 in Casino, New South Wales, Australia) is an Australian musician and actor. He was a member of the children's group The Wiggles from 1991-2012. Fatt was also a member of rock band The Cockroaches in the 1980s and 1990s. == References == == Other websites == * Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:Australian television actors Category:Actors from New South Wales Category:Singers from New South Wales Category:Australian pianists Category:Organists Category:Order of Australia
